4. Parameters:
   - `button_text` тЖТ `{{Click Text}}`
   - `button_url` тЖТ `{{Click URL}}`
   - `button_class` тЖТ `{{Click Classes}}`

5. Trigger: Use the **All Button Clicks** trigger.
6. Save & Publish.

